ImagePath +:$[FVWM_CACHEDIR]/icons:$[FVWM_DATADIR]/images:$[XDG_DATA_HOME]/ydesk/images:/usr/share/pixmaps
LocalePath @prefix@/share/locale;ydesk:+

PipeRead $[FVWM_LIBDIR]/infostore.sh

HideGeometryWindow

Emulate Win

SetAnimation 10

OpaqueMoveSize 0

EdgeScroll 0 0
EdgeResistance 500
EdgeThickness 1

IgnoreModifiers L25

DesktopSize $[infostore.ndesk]x1
DesktopName 0 "Y Desktop"
EwmhNumberOfDesktops 1

CursorStyle ROOT         left_ptr
CursorStyle TITLE        left_ptr
CursorStyle DEFAULT      left_ptr
CursorStyle SYS          left_ptr
CursorStyle MENU         left_ptr

BusyCursor DynamicMenu True, Read True

Style * EdgeMoveDelay 500
Style * EdgeMoveResistance 15
Style * ResizeOutline
Style * WindowShadeSteps 10
Style * ClickToFocus, MouseFocusClickRaises, GrabFocus
Style * MwmDecor, MwmFunctions
Style * CascadePlacement, UsePPosition
Style * HintOverride, !Icon, DecorateTransient
Style * MiniIcon default.png
